Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.37,0:01:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.30,0:01:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是初次见面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.38,0:01:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.38,0:01:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样拍片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.39,0:02:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水稀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.40,0:02:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.33,0:02:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天工作很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.34,0:02:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.34,0:02:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.34,0:02:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.28,0:02:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非得努力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.35,0:02:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你经验次数多少呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.36,0:02:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影也算的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.29,0:02:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.37,0:02:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.37,0:02:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让我有这么多学习机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.31,0:02:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.38,0:02:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.38,0:02:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.32,0:03:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜欢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.32,0:03:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.39,0:03:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的时候忍不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.39,0:03:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会很怀疑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.33,0:03:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己可以做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.34,0:03:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么性感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.28,0:03:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你会不安吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.29,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧张成份多一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.29,0:03:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得还是有点差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会害怕呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.36,0:03:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.30,0:03:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很相信你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.37,0:03:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟男优有交流吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.38,0:04:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现场的话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.39,0:04:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么想法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.39,0:04:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.34,0:04:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是好事情喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.34,0:04:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.28,0:04:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要多想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.28,0:04:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.28,0:04:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出全力即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.29,0:04:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都拿出全力呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点危险就是了
