Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:27.38,1:58:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:30.32,1:58:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一般的做爱不同吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:33.39,1:58:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:37.39,1:58:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:40.33,1:58:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:42.33,1:58:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很好的经验喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:44.33,1:58:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:47.40,1:58:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我也很希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:50.34,1:58:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有机会吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:54.34,1:58:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错就是这意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:57.28,1:59:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能暂时没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:00.35,1:59:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:05.28,1:59:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你好好冲澡
