Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:14.36,1:59:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:16.36,1:59:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:36.38,1:59:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗   拍什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:42.39,1:59:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:44.39,1:59:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:48.39,1:59:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:51.33,1:59:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:53.33,1:59:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:55.33,1:59:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是惊喜吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:58.40,2:00:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:02.27,2:00:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你的送别礼喔
