Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:09.35,2:00:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:12.28,2:00:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:16.29,2:00:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:19.36,2:00:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:26.30,2:00:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好奇妙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:32.30,2:00:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的纪念呀
